name: Space W.A.R.P.
description:
TEAM: GH-63+74

MEMBERS: Punya Aachman, Jivesh Piplani, Shivika Batra, Divyansh Kumar Pal, Kriti Goel

This is a thrilling adventure in space where you face many challenges that test your skills and bravery alike. It is a first person game which requires the player to be agile and smart in managing resources found on the planets.
